                <mxCell id="rm-bot-note" value="Framing for the conversation: this deck describes what we PLAN to build.&#10;Where things already exist (engine, bus, cache, knowledge store, RBAC, dev compose), it is at proof-of-mechanism scale — not production-onboarded with a real tenant, real IdP, or real SoR. Phase 2 closes those gaps; Phase 3 onboards the first tenant." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FEF3C7;strokeColor=#78350F;fontColor=#78350F;fontSize=12;" parent="1" vertex="1">
